title: Ryobi RY401017 40V HP Brushless 20 in. Cordless Battery Walk Behind Push Lawn Mower
description: Power through your yard work with the Ryobi RY401017 40V HP Brushless 20 in. Cordless Walk-Behind Push Lawn Mower. Designed for efficiency and convenience, this tool-only model features a powerful brushless motor, 20-inch cutting deck, and options for bagging, mulching, or side discharge. It offers a push-button start, compact storage, and high-performance mowing—perfect for small to medium-sized lawns. Battery and charger not included. Condition is open box, like new—tested for listing photos only.
